<i>noun</i>: 파국 [파ː국], 변란 [별ː란], 대참사 [대ː참사] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>파국 [파ː국]</dt><br>
<dd>catastrophe</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 사태가 잘못되어 망가져 버림. 또는 그 판국.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a certain matter or situation goes wrong and ends up being ruined, or such a situation.</dd><br>
<dt>변란 [별ː란]</dt><br>
<dd>upheaval; catastrophe</dd><br>
<dd>나라를 위험에 빠뜨릴 만큼 큰 재난이나 싸움.</dd><br>
<dd>A huge disaster or fight that can put a nation in a dangerous situation.</dd><br>
<dt>대참사 [대ː참사]</dt><br>
<dd>apocalypse; catastrophe; disaster</dd><br>
<dd>매우 비참하고 끔찍한 사건.</dd><br>
<dd>A very tragic, horrible incident.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>